Test
c
geometry 3
c
c
c Define hotspot (Hs) of DT (50 Micrometers)
c
DEFINE HsRad 0.01
DEFINE HsEndZone 100
DEFINE TotZone 200
DEFINE HsTemp 4
DEFINE HsDensity 100
c
c 200 zones of DT gas fisrt
c
MESH 1 HsEndZone+1 0 HsRad
MESH HsEndZone+1 TotZone HsRad .05
c
REGION 1 HsEndZone 1 HsDensity HsTemp
MATERIAL 1 1. 2. 1
MATERIAL 1 1. 3. 1
c
c Define Cold fuel (Cf)
c
DEFINE CfTemp 1e-4
c
REGION HsEndZone+1 TotZone 2 HsDensity CfTemp
MATERIAL 2 1. 2. 1
MATERIAL 2 1. 3. 1
c
c Use DT eos for Hs and Cf
c Use Saha ionization model for all regions
EOS 11 1 2
IONIZ 1 1
IONIZ 2 1
c 
c Extrapolate EOS linearly for high temperatures
c
EOSXTRP 1 2 2 2 2
EOSXTRP 2 2 2 2 2
c
c Turn on Thermonuclear burn in fuel regions
c
TNBURN 1 2
c
c Including ppf file output 
c
PPARRAY r rcm rho ti BPEPRD
PARM postdt 1e-13
c
PARM DTMIN 1.e-30
PARM tstop 8.e-10
PARM itmcyc 10
PARM NSTOP 60000
c